Package: deltafeedback
Version: @VERSION@
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Installed-Size: @INSTALLED_SIZE@
Maintainer: Roman <167345407+askhatovich@users.noreply.github.com>
Depends: libc6, libsqlite3-0, libssl3, adduser
Homepage: https://github.com/askhatovich/deltafeedback
Description: Self-hosted contact form with a Delta Chat bot backend.
 Visitors send messages via a tiny HTML form; messages are delivered to
 the operator over Delta Chat. Replies routed back through DC quote/reply
 appear on the visitor's ticket page.
 .
 POW captcha + honeypot + form fill-time check protect against trivial
 spam. Tickets are auto-purged after 7 days of inactivity.
